        "action": "Review discharge of mental health patients",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Why do we allow people struggling with mental health to be discharged alone. We think this is a huge safeguarding issue and not protecting the vulnerable. A review should consider requiring that patients are discharged into the care of someone. We think this could prevent the loss of lives.",
